<Layout title="Smart Stewards: Step 01 of The Stairway | Stairway Mortgage" description="The Stairway begins before you ever own a home. Smart Stewards is about teaching the next generation — and yourself — to treat money as something to s" canonical="https://stairwaymortgage.com/the-8-steps/smart-stewards/">
